'''上交叉綜合症'''（{{lang|en|upper crossed syndrome}}），俗称'''電腦肩'''、'''凝肩'''，泛指長期使用電腦造成[[肩周肌|肩周肌]]、[[肌腱|肌腱]]、[[滑囊|滑囊]]、[[關節囊|關節囊]]的腰酸背痛等疾病，主要由久坐造成，比如长时间使用电脑、长时间[[驾驶|驾驶]]、[[阅读|阅读]]等。可以通过脊骨矫正的方法治疗上交叉综合症<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/ad/Panadol0819/index.html?redirect=%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2Fad%2FPanadol0819%2Findex.html |title=紓緩電腦肩有法-東方日報 |access-date=2022-01-22 |archive-date=2020-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115010745/https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/ad/Panadol0819/index.html?redirect=%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2Fad%2FPanadol0819%2Findex.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="香港執業脊醫協會（C.D.A.H.K.）2015">{{cite book|author=香港執業脊醫協會（C.D.A.H.K.）|title=脊醫才會知的秘密！|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=XxaOCgAAQBAJ&pg=PA74|date=8 July 2015|publisher=Red Publish|isbn=978-988-14387-3-7|pages=74–76|access-date=2019-02-10|archive-date=2019-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190219020344/https://books.google.com/books?id=XxaOCgAAQBAJ&pg=PA74|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Jennifer Huizen|url=https://www.medicalnewstoday.com/articles/318897.php|title=What's to know about upper crossed syndrome?|website=Medical News Today|accessdate=2019-02-10|archive-date=2019-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190824070117/https://www.medicalnewstoday.com/articles/318897.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

